            },
            "mirrored": true,
            "semanticLabel": "The Queen"
          }
        ]
      },
      "frames": [
        {
          "id": "dawn-returns",
          "title": "Dawn Returns",
          "paragraphs": [
            "The knight breaks the Hollow Star. The eighth jewel wakes, and the completed Regalia shines across the throne hall.",
            "The dark wall around the Queen falls. Sunlight reaches the citadel, then the roads and homes of all eight realms."
          ],
          "semanticLabel": "The Hollow Star breaks and sunlight returns to the citadel.",
          "actionLabel": "See the dawn"
        },
        {
          "id": "the-knights-road",
          "title": "The Knight’s Road",
          "paragraphs": [
            "The knight returns the Regalia to the Queen. Together they open the gates between the realms again.",
            "The Queen offers the knight a place beside her. The knight thanks her, then chooses the open road. The people remember the knight who brought back the dawn."
          ],
